---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Martial Arts & TCM" description="Explore Chinese martial arts - from Shaolin Kung Fu to Tai Chi - and Traditional Chinese Medicine wisdom.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-600 via-emerald-600 to-green-700 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="text-green-200 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Health</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Martial Arts & TCM</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-green-100">The body is a temple, and Chinese wisdom knows how to care for it—through movement, breath, and the healing arts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/martial/kungfu" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🥋</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">Kung Fu Styles</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">From Shaolin's explosive power to Wing Chun's economy of motion—hundreds of fighting systems.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/martial/taichi" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">☯️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">Tai Chi</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">The gentle martial art that balances body and mind, now practiced worldwide for health.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/martial/tcm" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💊</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">Traditional Chinese Medicine</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Acupuncture, herbal medicine, and the philosophy of balancing yin and yang.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/martial/qigong" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌬️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">Qi Gong & Wellness</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Breath work, meditation, and exercises to cultivate vital energy (qi) for longevity.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-8">Featured Articles</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-emerald-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🏯</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Shaolin Temple: Birthplace of Kung Fu</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">The legend, history, and modern reality of China's most famous martial arts monastery.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-teal-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🧘</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Tai Chi for Beginners: Your First Steps</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Beginner's guide to the basic movements and philosophy of Tai Chi Chuan.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">💉</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Acupuncture: Ancient Wisdom Meets Modern Science</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">How tiny needles trigger the body's healing response.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
